  "_comment_architecture": [
    "Battery commissioning event with product, location, and organization master data inline.",
    "masterDataAvailableFor carries:",
    "  - gs1: product master data (productName, gtin, netWeight, countryOfOrigin, regulatoryInformation)",
    "  - battery:-prefixed PRODUCT-LEVEL attributes (batteryCategory, batteryChemistry, ratedCapacity,",
    "    ratedEnergy) — these describe the GTIN and are identical across every lot of this SKU.",
    "    GS1 has no native term for them yet; keeping them in the product entry means any downstream",
    "    consumer gets the full product card in one place.",
    "ilmd is INTENTIONALLY ABSENT: we have no lot-specific data to assert on this event.",
    "Observation-specific readings (stateOfHealth, stateOfCharge, cycleCount at this moment) ride",
    "in sensorElementList, the EPCIS-native place for sensor observations.",
    "",
    "HTTP header: GS1-Extensions: dpp=https://ref.openepcis.io/extensions/common/core/,battery=https://ref.openepcis.io/extensions/eu/battery/",
    "See: extensions/common/core/docs/EPCIS_MASTERDATA_AND_EXTENSIONS.md",
    "GS1 demo prefix 952 (7-digit GCP: 9521234)."
  ],
